---
---

<main class="page">
  <nav class="nav">
    <div class="brand">NEXOR <span>//</span></div>

   <div class="nav-links">
  <a href="#signals">Signals</a>
  <a href="#archive">Archive</a>
  <a href="#operators">Operators</a>
  <a href="#bridge">AXYRO</a>
</div>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="signal-label">
      <span></span>
      Signal Layer // Future Gaming & Compute Culture
    </div>

    <h1>
      Future Gaming<br />
      & Compute Signals
    </h1>

    <p>
      Tracking the culture around future systems, sharper setups,
      software, hardware and digital environments.
    </p>

    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="#signals">Explore Signals</a>
      <a href="#bridge" class="ghost">AXYRO Bridge</a>
    </div>

    <div class="signal-lines">
      <span></span>
      <span></span>
      <span></span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="signals" class="cards">
    <article class="featured">
      <span>01 / Future Setups</span>
      <h2>Clean machines.<br />Sharper environments.</h2>
      <p>
        NEXOR tracks the shift away from loud gaming rooms toward
        focused operator-grade setups and calmer digital workspaces.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article>
      <span>02 / Software Critique</span>
      <h2>Most software became louder than useful.</h2>
      <p>
        Interfaces are becoming noisy. NEXOR follows the tools that
        reduce friction instead of adding more.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="tall">
      <span>03 / Compute Culture</span>
      <h2>The next gaming culture is not RGB.</h2>
      <p>
        Future gaming is moving toward cleaner systems, calmer
        environments and sharper taste.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="wide">
      <span>04 / Signal Layer</span>
      <h2>
        Hardware.<br />
        Interfaces.<br />
        Operator culture.
      </h2>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section id="operators" class="feed">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Operator Environments</p>
      <h2>Signal over noise.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="feed-grid">
      <div>Hardware Radar</div>
      <div>Interface Studies</div>
      <div>Setup Culture</div>
      <div>Weird Tech</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="stream">
   <div class="signal-stream">

  <article class="stream-card large">
    <span>SIGNAL 0021 / MAY 2026 / INTERFACE STUDY</span>
    <h3>Why gaming setups are becoming quieter.</h3>
  </article>

  <article class="stream-card">
    <span>SIGNAL 0018 / SETUP CULTURE</span>
    <h3>Most gaming rooms are evolving into operator environments.</h3>
  </article>

  <article class="stream-card">
    <span>SIGNAL 0015 / SOFTWARE</span>
    <h3>Modern interfaces mistake stimulation for innovation.</h3>
  </article>

  <article class="stream-card wide-card">
    <span>SIGNAL 0011 / FUTURE COMPUTE</span>
    <h3>
      AI PCs, calmer systems and darker environments are reshaping
      future compute culture.
    </h3>
  </article>
    </div>
  </section>

<section id="archive" class="archive">
    <div class="archive-top">
      <div>
        <p>Signal Archive</p>
        <h2>Future systems are becoming quieter.</h2>
      </div>

      <span class="archive-status">LIVE SIGNALS / CURATED FEED</span>
    </div>

    <div class="archive-grid">
      <article class="archive-card large-card">
        <div class="archive-meta">
          <span>SETUP SIGNAL</span>
          <span>01</span>
        </div>

        <h3>Operator-grade setups are replacing RGB gaming rooms.</h3>

        <p>
          The next generation of gaming environments will feel darker,
          calmer and more intentional.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="archive-card">
        <div class="archive-meta">
          <span>INTERFACE STUDY</span>
          <span>02</span>
        </div>

        <h3>Most modern software became overstimulated.</h3>
      </article>

      <article class="archive-card">
        <div class="archive-meta">
          <span>COMPUTE CULTURE</span>
          <span>03</span>
        </div>

        <h3>Future systems need calmer visual environments.</h3>
      </article>

      <article class="archive-card wide-archive">
        <div class="archive-meta">
          <span>NEXOR //</span>
          <span>LIVE</span>
        </div>

        <h3>
          Tracking the culture around future hardware, software,
          interfaces and digital operator environments.
        </h3>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="signals-strip">
    <div class="signals-head">
      <p>Latest Signals</p>
      <span>LIVE FEED / CURATED OBSERVATIONS</span>
    </div>

    <div class="signals-list">
      <article>
        <span>SETUP CULTURE</span>
        <h3>Gaming rooms are shifting toward calmer operator environments.</h3>
      </article>

      <article>
        <span>INTERFACE SIGNAL</span>
        <h3>Most modern interfaces are optimized for stimulation instead of clarity.</h3>
      </article>

      <article>
        <span>FUTURE HARDWARE</span>
        <h3>AI PCs will reshape workstation culture faster than gaming culture expects.</h3>
      </article>

      <article>
        <span>NEXOR //</span>
        <h3>Future compute culture is becoming darker, quieter and more intentional.</h3>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="bridge" class="bridge">
    <div class="bridge-inner">
      <p>AXYRO Bridge</p>

      <h2>
        AXYRO is the silent core.<br />
        NEXOR // is the signal layer.
      </h2>

      <span>
        One builds the environment. The other tracks the culture forming around it.
      </span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="support">
  <div class="support-inner">
    <p>Support The Signal</p>

    <h2>
      Independent signal needs independent support.
    </h2>

    <span>
      NEXOR is built independently. Support helps fund future signal
      studies, hardware culture and calmer digital environments.
    </span>

    <div class="support-actions">

  <a href="#" class="btc-button" id="open-btc-modal">
  <img src="/btc-icon.png" alt="BTC" />
  Support via Lightning
</a>

      <a
        href="https://buymeacoffee.com/nexorsignal"
        target="_blank"
        class="coffee-button"
      >
        <img src="/coffee-icon.png" alt="Coffee" />
        Buy Me A Coffee
      </a>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="btc-modal" id="btc-modal">
  <div class="btc-modal-card">
  <button class="btc-close" id="close-btc-modal">//</button>

    <p>Lightning Support</p>

    <h3>Scan to support NEXOR //</h3>

    <img class="btc-qr" src="/lightning-qr.png" alt="Lightning QR Code" />

    <button class="copy-lightning" id="copy-lightning">
      Copy Lightning Invoice
    </button>
  </div>
</div>
</main>

<style>
  :global(html) {
  scroll-behavior: smooth;
}
  :global(*) {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  :global(body) {
    margin: 0;
    background: #050608;
    color: #f5f7fa;
    font-family:
      Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont,
      "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
  }

  .page {
    min-height: 100vh;
    overflow: hidden;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 70% 18%, rgba(183, 255, 60, 0.13), transparent 28%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 15% 85%, rgba(90, 120, 255, 0.08), transparent 32%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #050608 0%, #071016 48%, #050608 100%);
  }

  .page::before {
    content: "";
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.035) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.035) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 64px 64px;
    mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, black 18%, black 72%, transparent);
    opacity: 0.18;
  }

  .page::after {
    content: "";
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    background:
      linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 0%, rgba(183, 255, 60, 0.025) 48%, transparent 100%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 72% 22%, rgba(183, 255, 60, 0.1), transparent 22%);
    opacity: 0.9;
    mix-blend-mode: screen;
  }

  .nav {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 40px));
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 28px 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .brand {
    letter-spacing: 0.28em;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .brand span {
    color: #b7ff3c;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  .nav-links a {
    color: rgba(245, 247, 250, 0.56);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .hero {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 40px));
    margin: 0 auto;
     padding: 120px 0 90px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .signal-label {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    color: rgba(245, 247, 250, 0.58);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .signal-label span {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #b7ff3c;
    box-shadow: 0 0 22px rgba(183, 255, 60, 0.75);
  }

  h1 {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 28px 0 0;
    font-size: clamp(58px, 9vw, 132px);
    line-height: 0.9;
    letter-spacing: -0.075em;
    font-weight: 760;
  }

  .hero p {
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-top: 32px;
    color: rgba(245, 247, 250, 0.62);
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    animation: heroReveal 1.8s ease forwards;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(18px);
  }

  .hero-actions {
    margin-top: 38px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .hero-actions a {
    padding: 13px 18px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #b7ff3c;
    color: #050608;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .hero-actions .ghost {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.045);
    color: rgba(245, 247, 250, 0.82);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  }

  .signal-lines {
    position: absolute;
    top: 120px;
    right: -120px;
    width: 540px;
    height: 540px;
    pointer-events: none;
    opacity: 0.35;
  }

  .signal-lines span {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border: 1px solid rgba(183, 255, 60, 0.08);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .signal-lines span:nth-child(1) {
    transform: scale(1);
  }

  .signal-lines span:nth-child(2) {
    transform: scale(1.22);
  }

  .signal-lines span:nth-child(3) {
    transform: scale(1.44);
  }

  .cards,
  .feed,
  .stream,
  .archive,
  .signals-strip,
  .bridge {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 40px));
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 14px;
    padding-bottom: 90px;
  }

  article {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    min-height: 260px;
    padding: 28px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.018)),
      #0b1016;
    border-radius: 28px;
    box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28);
    transition:
    transform 0.35s ease,
    border-color 0.35s ease,
    background 0.35s ease;
  }

  article::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(183, 255, 60, 0.08), transparent 36%);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.45s ease;
  }

  article:hover::before {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  article span {
    color: #b7ff3c;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.13em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  article h2 {
    margin: 46px 0 0;
    font-size: 26px;
    line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  }

  article p {
    margin-top: 18px;
    color: rgba(245, 247, 250, 0.54);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .featured {
    grid-column: span 2;
    min-height: 340px;
  }

  .featured h2 {
    font-size: 54px;
    max-width: 540px;
  }

  .tall {
    min-height: 340px;
  }

  .wide {
    grid-column: span 2;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(183, 255, 60, 0.08), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02)),
      #10161d;
  }

  .wide h2 {
    max-width: 620px;
    font-size: 58px;
    line-height: 0.92;
  }

  .feed {
    padding: 70px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.3fr;
    gap: 44px;
  }

  .eyebrow,
  .stream-header p,
  .archive-top p,
  .signals-head p,
  .bridge p {
    color: #b7ff3c;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  .feed h2,
  .bridge h2 {
    margin: 12px 0 0;
    font-size: clamp(42px, 6vw, 86px);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.065em;
  }

  .feed-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .feed-grid div {
    min-height: 110px;
    padding: 22px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    background: #10161d;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
    color: rgba(245, 247, 250, 0.72);
    transition:
    transform 0.35s ease,
    border-color 0.35s ease,
    background 0.35s ease;
  }
  .feed-grid div:hover {
  transform: translateY(-3px);
  border-color: rgba(183,255,60,0.16);
  background: #121922;
}

  .stream {
     padding: 70px 0 120px;
  }

  .stream-header {
    max-width: 760px;
  }

  .stream-header h2 {
    margin-top: 18px;
    font-size: clamp(42px, 5vw, 76px);
    line-height: 0.96;
    letter-spacing: -0.06em;
  }

  .stream-grid {
    margin-top: 52px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    gap: 14px;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  .stream-card {
    min-height: 220px;
  }

  .stream-card h3 {
    margin-top: 42px;
    max-width: 520px;
    font-size: 34px;
    line-height: 1.02;
    letter-spacing: -0.05em;
  }

  .stream-card.large {
    min-height: 320px;
  }

  .stream-card:not(.large):not(.wide-card) h3 {
    font-size: 28px;
  }

  .wide-card {
    grid-column: span 2;
    min-height: 220px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(183, 255, 60, 0.06), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02)),
      #10161d;
  }

  .wide-card h3 {
    max-width: 900px;
    font-size: 42px;
  }

  .archive {
    padding: 20px 0 140px;
  }

  .archive-top {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .archive-top h2 {
    margin-top: 16px;
    max-width: 760px;
    font-size: clamp(42px, 5vw, 78px);
    line-height: 0.94;
    letter-spacing: -0.065em;
  }

  .archive-status {
    color: rgba(245, 247, 250, 0.48);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
  }

  .archive-grid {
    margin-top: 56px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .archive-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    color: #b7ff3c;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .archive-card h3 {
    margin-top: 42px;
    font-size: 34px;
    line-height: 1.02;
    letter-spacing: -0.05em;
  }

  .archive-card p {
    margin-top: 20px;
    max-width: 540px;
    color: rgba(245, 247, 250, 0.56);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .large-card {
    grid-column: span 2;
    min-height: 320px;
  }

  .large-card h3 {
    max-width: 720px;
    font-size: 52px;
  }

  .wide-archive {
    grid-column: span 2;
    min-height: 220px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(183, 255, 60, 0.07), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02)),
      #10161d;
  }

  .wide-archive h3 {
    max-width: 860px;
    font-size: 40px;
  }

  .signals-strip {
    padding: 10px 0 140px;
  }

  .signals-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 24px;
    padding-bottom: 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  }

  .signals-head span {
    color: rgba(245, 247, 250, 0.45);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
  }

  .signals-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .signals-list article {
    min-height: 180px;
    padding: 34px 0;
    border: 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    background: transparent;
    border-radius: 0;
    box-shadow: none;
  }

  .signals-list article::before {
    display: none;
  }

  .signals-list article h3 {
    margin-top: 20px;
    max-width: 980px;
    font-size: clamp(34px, 4vw, 58px);
    line-height: 0.96;
    letter-spacing: -0.06em;
    transition:
      transform 0.35s ease,
      color 0.35s ease;
  }

  .signals-list article:hover h3 {
    transform: translateX(10px);
    color: #b7ff3c;
  }

  .bridge {
    padding: 120px 0 160px;
  }

  .bridge-inner {
    padding: 46px;
    border-radius: 34px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(183, 255, 60, 0.08), transparent 34%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.055), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.018)),
      #0b1016;
  }

  .bridge h2 {
    margin: 22px 0 0;
    max-width: 960px;
    font-size: clamp(42px, 5.8vw, 86px);
    line-height: 0.94;
    letter-spacing: -0.065em;
  }

  .bridge span {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 28px;
    max-width: 620px;
    color: rgba(245, 247, 250, 0.58);
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    .nav-links {
      display: none;
      transition:
      color 0.3s ease,
       opacity 0.3s ease;
    }
   .nav-links a:hover {
    color: #b7ff3c;
}
    .hero {
      padding-top: 90px;
    }

    h1 {
      letter-spacing: -0.055em;
      animation: heroReveal 1.4s ease forwards;
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(18px);
    }

    .cards,
    .feed,
    .stream-grid,
    .archive-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .featured,
    .wide,
    .wide-card,
    .large-card,
    .wide-archive {
      grid-column: span 1;
    }

    .featured h2,
    .wide h2,
    .wide-card h3,
    .large-card h3,
    .wide-archive h3,
    .archive-card h3,
    .stream-card h3 {
      font-size: 34px;
    }

    .archive-top,
    .signals-head {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    article {
      min-height: 230px;
    }

    .feed-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .signals-list article {
      min-height: 140px;
    }

    .bridge-inner {
      padding: 30px;
    }
  }
  @keyframes heroReveal {
  to {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
}
.signal-stream {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
  gap: 22px;
  margin-top: 64px;
}

.stream-card {
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  min-height: 220px;
  padding: 34px;
  border-radius: 28px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  background:
    linear-gradient(
      145deg,
      rgba(18,24,36,0.92),
      rgba(8,12,18,0.96)
    );
  transition:
    transform 0.35s ease,
    border-color 0.35s ease,
    background 0.35s ease;
}

.stream-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px);
  border-color: rgba(183,255,60,0.16);
}

.stream-card span {
  color: #b7ff3c;
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.16em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.stream-card h3 {
  margin-top: 32px;
  max-width: 560px;
  font-size: 40px;
  line-height: 1.04;
  letter-spacing: -0.05em;
}

.stream-card.large {
  min-height: 320px;
}

.wide-card {
  grid-column: span 2;
  min-height: 240px;
}

.wide-card h3 {
  max-width: 900px;
}
.support {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
  width: min(980px, calc(100% - 40px));
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 20px 0 180px;
}

.support-inner {
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  padding: 58px;
  border-radius: 34px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  background:
    radial-gradient(
